'''Castle Ventress''' was [[Asajj Ventress/Legends|Asajj Ventress's]] citadel on the planet [[Rattatak/Legends|Rattatak]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It was her base of operations and a prison to many [[Rattataki/Legends|Rattataki]]. She kept the [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsabers]] of her [[Death/Legends|dead]] [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]], [[Ky Narec/Legends|Ky Narec]], housed within the halls of the citadel, along with a statue of him.

During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Advanced Recon Commando/Legends|ARC trooper]] [[Alpha (Advanced Recon Commando)|Alpha-17]] were held in the castle's prison, where they were [[Torture/Legends|tortured]] by Ventress after the [[Battle of Jabiim]]. They eventually [[Escape from Rattatak|escaped]] after stealing Ky Narec's lightsaber and one of Ventress's [[Ginivex-class starfighter/Legends|''Ginivex''-class starfighters]].

